title: Go get my lunch & Team of ATL deliberation
itunes:title: Go get my lunch & Team of ATL deliberation
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – break down all the latest news from around the NFL including newfound heat between Bills head coach Rex Ryan and with Seahawks head coach Pete Carroll after Seattle’s victory on Monday night. Then, Marc Sessler has an announcement that could shake up the entire foundation of the Team of ATL. Plus, the heroes throw out a few midseason sandwich props before recapping the Thursday night matchup between the Browns and the Ravens.
